She looked at the sky and then to Rex. She could tell he didn't want 
to be there. She turned and walked back into the ship. She said in a 
soft spoken voice, "I'll not bother you any more.  I'll go back to 
back to my room now." She started to walked down the hall and towards 
her quarters.
